{"tid":335803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"躲女廁偷窺被逮認「我是變態」　他「用肉眼看」不起訴","createTime":"2017-07-26T01:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T10:36:46.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac9aced6a081e874724ef6e8ca4457212aa896b","tid":335803,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"桃園市中壢區一名36歲的李姓男子遭指控在公園女廁偷窺，當場被逮住時也坦承「我是變態，性生活不協調」，然而，因為他並沒有使用手機等工具偷拍，在妨害秘密罪部分事證不足獲不起訴。但「用肉眼看」的部分則，檢方將函請警方依社會秩序維護法裁罰，最高恐面臨6000元罰鍰。<br />\n<br />\n黃姓女子今年5月和男友一起到中壢某處公園遊玩，期間跑去上廁所卻發現隔間上有數個破洞，但部分洞口都被用衛生紙塞住，再仔細一看發現隔壁間似乎有黑影在晃動，於是趕忙向在外頭等著的男友求救，最後順利將躲在裡頭的李男制伏。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">李男辯稱，當天是因為肚子痛跑錯廁所，等到發現時黃女已經進入廁所，他想出去又怕尷尬，只好先用衛生紙把洞塞住，沒想到還是被發現，接著就被對方男友逮住，並在遭逼迫的情況下坦承自己是變態、性生活不協調，最後以1萬元私下和解。</span><br />\n<br />\n桃園地檢署檢察官認為，李男並未使用手機等工具偷拍，因此沒有觸犯妨害秘密罪，在這部分給予不起訴處分；至於「用肉眼看」的偷窺部分，則會函請警方進一步調查，如果屬實，將依違反社會秩序維護法進行裁罰，最高可能面臨6000元罰鍰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://giant.gfycat.com/InfiniteDimwittedAnt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiant.gfycat.com%2FInfiniteDimwittedAnt.gif&h=70116f89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d01b05434a3e52cc1e5096f244a101b944e75c08","tid":335803,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:29:08.000Z","msg":"唔入不誠實使用電腦咪入遊蕩"},{"pid":"8655bb9a160e716fbc6d79437ac54ac443b34ab2","tid":335803,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:30:55.000Z","msg":"入黎係睇gif"},{"pid":"8827dcb1a2eea22ecc56e291c5dc0c8d27c01645","tid":335803,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"glory hole"},{"pid":"318e0640f199940cc452157981c65983309d1973","tid":335803,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:38:37.000Z","msg":"ddg好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d141bfcee6d5c7df49bb68ce56dc909064942033","tid":335803,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:42:52.000Z","msg":"和解完都告咁撚仆街"},{"pid":"cf2ae272373b8d604d2d38ad6d687386a1eba56b","tid":335803,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入黎係睇gif</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf6f9a52eb682abaeddf51a5b22dee8fbb4fadb","tid":335803,"uid":56452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"ddg 勁撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582146d6759af456c0840ab0ce1c553475df9b39","tid":335803,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"d女人好撚古惑架"},{"pid":"f056167b4bed185e430a7dcca39b3c8f7e7615df","tid":335803,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"用肉眼看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e9385e0a2558d6bbd6ee7ec3a77fde25263a94","tid":335803,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"@dassada<br />\n學野"}]}